description: [BrazzersExxtra] Natalia Starr - The Daily Special (20.08.2017) Natalia's a pin-up goddess and Charles is a greaser—and both are straight out of your 1950s wet dream. Natalia is closing up at the diner when an attractive customer comes in. When Charles asks to hear the daily specials, she decides to seduce him with a secret dessert only on offer to the most notable customers. Taking her advice, he orders it and gets a lot more than just a delicious treat—two sweet creampies for the price of one!
